1. *Čitav* dan je bio oblačan. (The whole day was cloudy.)
2. On je pio *čitavu* čašu. (He drank the whole glass.)
3. *Čitavim* se danima igrala igrica. (She played the game for days on end.)
4. *Čitavim* putem je pričala o tome. (She talked about it the whole way.)
5. *Čitavu* noć smo se zabavljali. (We had a great time the whole night.) 
6. *Čitavu* smo godinu planirali. (We planned the whole year.)